%% Diagram: Service Worker lifecycle
%% Type: stateDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Parsed: register(scriptURL)
    Parsed --> Installing: install event
    Installing --> Installed: precache complete
    Installing --> Redundant: install rejected
    Installed --> Activating: activate event
    Activating --> Activated: claim() resolved
    Activated --> Dormant: idle ~30s
    Dormant --> Activated: next event<br/>(fetch / push / msg)
    Activated --> Redundant: new SW activated
    Dormant --> Redundant: new SW activated
    Redundant --> [*]
